   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>Subject Two Hundred Three THE LAMB THAT WAS SLAIN Scripture: Rev 5:6, 9; 1:5; 7:14, 17; 13:8 The Lamb is Christ Christ came to redeem men.</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>Christ s redemption was accomplished through His coming as the Lamb of God.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>As the Lamb He was slain and His blood was shed for men.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>To be slain is to be crucified Christ was crucified on the cross because He bore man s sins.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>Christ was crucified to satisfy God s righteous requirement.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>The effectiveness of the Lamb s being slain It enables us to depart from sins.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>It washes us clean and white.</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>It qualifies us to receive the life of God.</S>
   <S PAR='9' RSNT='1' SNO='9'>How to obtain the Lamb that was slain Confess that He was slain for you.</S>
   <S PAR='10' RSNT='1' SNO='10'>Receive Him as your Savior.</S>
   </TEXT>
